WEBVTT

07:25.230 --> 07:27.330 line:80%
It is a blessing for the people.

07:27.670 --> 07:30.140 line:80%
In his youth,
Xie Zheng, the Marquis of Wu'an,

07:30.140 --> 07:32.880 line:80%
led troops to avenge
the humiliation at Jinzhou.

07:33.070 --> 07:36.010 line:80%
The Beijue people
tremble at the mention of his name.
